item.title: Twenty One Pilots - Chlorine - Key of C
item.description:
This tutorial will show you how to play Chlorine on the ukulele by Twenty One Pilots. The chords used are C F G Am.
If you found this video useful please subscribe and share with your friends. If you want to be notified of future videos please click on bell next to subscribe.
Video created on the iPad Pro using Luma Fusion. The uke chord font is Chordette for Education, available at ukefarm.com.

item.title: Twenty One Pilots - House Of Gold - Key of C
item.description:
Ukulele play along
House Of Gold - Twenty One Pilots
Using the chords: C F G A7 Am Dm Bbm ** A good chance to practice the B flat minor chord! **
Suggested Strum Patterns: D DU U DU or D DU DU DU - it is fast
Notes: Tyler Joseph plays a C chord for the first section (chorus). I have used the chords as a guide to help singing but you can play a C chord if you prefer.
This video is meant for educational purposes.
No copyright infringement intended
